<tr><td class="maintext"><b>AdSapient Inc.'s Commitment to Privacy</b></td></tr>
<tr>
	<td class="maintext">
	  AdSapient Inc. is firmly committed to protecting the privacy of Internet users and fostering consumer confidence in the Internet, Internet advertising and direct marketing. We invite all users to contact us at contact@adsapient.com with any questions or concerns.
	</td>
